        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="L-c2-l" value="&lt;b&gt;atomic skill + path-scoped rules&lt;/b&gt; (青) — .claude/skills/ (12 atomic、AI auto-trigger or user /name) + .claude/rules/&amp;lt;topic&amp;gt;-discipline.md (2、paths frontmatter で matching file 時のみ load、ADR-0024)。orchestration only、規約本文は docs/rules/ 参照 (ADR-0018)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="L1">
